## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not capture the full scope of how LinkedIn Learning is utilized across all industries. Additionally, the information is limited to what is publicly shared by companies and may not reflect proprietary or internal uses of the platform. Further research, including interviews with corporate training managers, could provide deeper insights into specific use cases and outcomes.